cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SD 

This paper deals with the problem of fraud detection in online systems, specifically search rank fraud. It involves the study of user behavior and the development of a fraud de-anonymization system. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). However, it also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and social networks (cs.SI) as it deals with the behavior of users in online systems. Additionally, it involves machine learning (cs.CY) and data structures and algorithms (cs.SD) in the development of the fraud de-anonymization system.
